    march_idea11_body: "The Global Gateway Initiative bundles €300 billion for investments in Africa by 2027. Return: long-term supply contracts for critical raw materials. Not a development-aid model — strategic economic access to the world's fastest growing region.",
    march_idea12_title: "Less bureaucracy, more output.",
    march_idea12_body: "Germany lost over 30 % of its solar-module production to China in 2024 — not because of weaker technology but because of four-year approval procedures. Outcome funding instead of input control: four months instead of four years. Smart system architecture, not deregulation.",
